{"tid":84590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英最後施政報告：拆灣仔運動場起新會展","createTime":"2017-01-17T15:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T03:06:30.000Z","uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7b515dcc7f298425a9eff49d38859a04ffbb379","tid":84590,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20150114/large/1421230410_41f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20150114%2Flarge%2F1421230410_41f1.jpg&h=4225f82b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首梁振英最後一份《施政報告》明日公佈，無綫新聞傍晚引述消息指，政府研究在灣仔運動場的現址，興建新會議展覽中心。 <br />\n<br />\n行政長官梁振英明日將會宣讀任內最後一份《施政報告》。無綫新聞引述消息指，灣仔會展雖然目前正在擴建，但政府將在《施政報告》中提出計劃在灣仔運動場，興建新的會議展覽中心。"},{"pid":"7ac16fb8764dd1bb59dd1383b82670617bfaf8d1","tid":84590,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:57:28.000Z","msg":"689死都要搞屎棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d610d13afbef19a757dad6a61bd0f988996a32b","tid":84590,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:58:28.000Z","msg":"死前都要搞屎棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「體育界沒有任何經濟貢獻」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6c136b0df45b873d97d227d8f999fba3159efd","tid":84590,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:58:33.000Z","msg":"拆埋關口"},{"pid":"ea88e8af415c1815e1eac1e2f54d5c3a4e23447a","tid":84590,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9c4c167df8ff9288f3264de9f918fb10ffbb64","tid":84590,"uid":33640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"